[Main]
Name=LO_WORD
Type=Function
Subtype=Macro
Header Files=dialogs.h
Definition=short LO_WORD (long);
Real Definition=#define LO_WORD(val) ((unsigned short) (val))

[Description]
Returns the low word from a long value.

[Explanation]
This function returns the lowest short value (the 16 least significant bits) of a long value. This macro function was created for <A HREF="$$LINK(DialogNew)">DialogNew</A>.